divs: Sighting DetailsAt the intersection of 119th and Andreson Blvd. my witness and I experienced a house size crop circle with two attached smaller circles, which was across the street from the Chevron, facing west. My high school friends son and I were placing garage sale sale signs on foot in that intersection, and easily noticed a perfect circle in the tall grass feild next to the road which was smashed perfectly down to the ground. I believe it was a crop circle and so does he. We naturally reported it to our families and friends, but this is my first public anouncement of it. I felt excited and reved up about it along with all the other strange extraterrestrial and paranormal happenings that happened to me that year.
